`_rdft` comes from fftw library.

My solution is downloading fftw and link with it, please see my fork:
 
https://github.com/syoyo/tensorflow/commit/d4ba9c8e9387b5ad62511aaa95adb2427d3d9952#diff-57135143920cd34bc2ac188b5934308eR82

For `_cblas_sgemm`, you may solve it by linking with BLAS library provided by iOS SDK, but I'm not sure.
